{"tid":2257840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美副國安顧問：京毀兩制剝奪港自治","createTime":"2020-10-25T14:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T14:59:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d9d25a984816937f2727e334faec1e881cdeca","tid":2257840,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/BFWEN4IRHZDRPOX6TP67KLEBBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FBFWEN4IRHZDRPOX6TP67KLEBBE%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=06497f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FBFWEN4IRHZDRPOX6TP67KLEBBE%2F&h=552fb000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/BFWEN4IRHZDRPOX6TP67KLEBBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美副國安顧問：京毀兩制剝奪港自治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C-oqMfOthguzbL0lmom8K1vnqGw=/981x736/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZXQVKCGHMFBSVEQYGRDUYBNAVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC-oqMfOthguzbL0lmom8K1vnqGw%3D%2F981x736%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZXQVKCGHMFBSVEQYGRDUYBNAVQ.jpg&h=3f97db61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■博明前日在英國智庫論壇演講斥中國不擇手段。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n美國特朗普政府著名「中國通」、美國副國家安全顧問博明（Matthew Pottinger）周五發表視像演說，用流利的普通話批評中國正利用極其純熟的統戰手段及金錢，令國際社會迎合北京利益。他指當中共發現如斯手段達不到目的，就會訴諸恐嚇和脅迫，並以香港去年的反修例運動為例，指北京最終就選擇拆毀一國兩制框架，剝奪香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n博明上周五通過視頻連線在英國智庫「政策交流」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轟中共訴諸恐嚇脅迫<br />\n<br />\n博明又指「當騙術達不到目的，中共經常訴諸恐嚇和脅迫」。他指，去年香港反修例運動抵抗北京實施更嚴酷的控制，為此北京採取了「拆毀了鄧小平一國兩制的框架，剝奪了使香港成為亞洲最興旺城市的自治」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，意大利外交部與國會近日委託智。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指中國一直想將台灣納入管轄，但在香港爆發反送中抗爭之後，此。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音/中央社"},{"pid":"d914b1d7cf8d6598aa2f2beef7ff48ce25d54ea1","tid":2257840,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"知啦!"},{"pid":"d1283f97a88c003b69d0a713b388c22ebdce2b0f","tid":2257840,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"SPEECH LINK?"},{"pid":"01fa817001357c07d7729ed49e1e6b44a7714705","tid":2257840,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"English vision?"},{"pid":"f213f6b95caf940ba1dcefb26e02a3eaca6055f1","tid":2257840,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"佢上次用國語講54<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65ad561d2661b2616d642e3657f64cbf7712d4e","tid":2257840,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}